ModelObject Edge Relation Object for mapping the Model/Key Pair A -> Model/Key Pair B Additionally a relationship type may be specified, this Model is a utility object for those wishing to represent data stores appropriate for Graph Databases
Group
Group objects represent a group object usually used by Authentication storage for the backend router services
ModelIterator
ModelIterator for implements Java STD Iterator for ModelObjects, allows for rudimentary DFS traversal of the JSON Tree
ModelKeys
ModelKeys is a static final class used by the database and other modules for a representation of the collection of model objects available.
